## Ghana Data Protection Act 843 (2012)
- [Data Protection Commission](https://www.dpc.gov.gh/)
- [Guidelines](https://www.dpc.gov.gh/index.php/guidelines/)
- **Enforcer:** Data Protection Commission
- **Penalties:** Fines + imprisonment
- **Report:** dataprotection.org.gh
